{"word":"G4285 - προηγέομαι - proēgéomai - pro-ay-geh'-om-ahee - Prefer","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προηγέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">proēgéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-ay-geh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Prefer</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முந்திக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"to go before and show the way, to go before and lead, to go before as leader"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2233 - ἡγέομαι - hēgéomai - hayg-eh'-om-ahee/2233\">G2233</a>; to <i>lead the way</i> for others, that is, <i>show deference:</i> - prefer.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1335/1335\">G1335</a>, <a href=\"#/G1834/1834\">G1834</a>, <a href=\"#/G2233/2233\">G2233</a>, <a href=\"#/G4285/4285\">G4285</a>"}]}